Bool version 0.000_01
=======================

Boolean constants and modifier.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Carp
    Const::Fast

